sources.title: Momotarô: Umi no shinpei (1945)
sources.description: A monkey, a dog, a pheasant, and a bear travel southward after resting in their villages at the foot of Mt. Fuji. A squadron flies to Onigashima under the command of Momotarou. Parachutes blossom in the sky. Momotarou and company will take over the island after a swift and successful mission. The village children pretend parachuting with glee as they run towards Mt. Fuji. Watch on RetroFlix.org:  https://retroflix.org/momotaro-umi-no-shinpei-1945/
